\#\#\# Top Answer: You can condition on the dimension using the class\-provided `\ifCLASSOPTIONonecolumn`:

```
\includegraphics
  [width = \ifCLASSOPTIONonecolumn .4\linewidth\else.9\linewidth\fi]
